,"ἐκ","ἐγώ"],"tr":"now [I] rejoice, not because [you all] were distressed, rather because you [all] were distressed into [a] change of mind, for [you all] were grieved according to God so that in no [thing you all] might be forfeited out of us.","para":null,"para_continued":false,"words":[{"form":"νῦν","lemma":"νῦν","type":"adverb","code":"D"},{"form":"χαίρω,","lemma":"χαίρω","type":"verb","code":"V"},{"form":"οὐχ","lemma":"οὐ","type":"adverb","code":"D"},{"form":"ὅτι","lemma":"ὅτι","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"ἐλυπήθητε,","lemma":"λυπέω","type":"verb","code":"V"},{"form":"ἀλλ’","lemma":"ἀλλά","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"ὅτι","lemma":"ὅτι","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"ἐλυπήθητε","lemma":"λυπέω","type":"verb","code":"V"},{"form":"εἰς","lemma":"εἰς","type":"preposition","code":"P"},{"form":"μετάνοιαν,","lemma":"μετάνοια","type":"noun","code":"N"},{"form":"ἐλυπήθητε","lemma":"λυπέω","type":"verb","code":"V"},{"form":"γὰρ","lemma":"γάρ","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"κατὰ","lemma":"κατά","type":"preposition","code":"P"},{"form":"θεόν,","lemma":"θεός","type":"noun","code":"N"},{"form":"ἵνα","lemma":"ἵνα","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"ἐν","lemma":"ἐν","type":"preposition","code":"P"},{"form":"μηδενὶ","lemma":"μηδείς","type":"adjective","code":"A"},{"form":"ζημιωθῆτε","lemma":"ζημιόω","type":"verb","code":"V"},{"form":"ἐξ","lemma":"ἐκ","type":"preposition","code":"P"},{"form":"ἡμῶν.","lemma":"ἐγώ","type":"personal_pronoun","code":"RP"}]},{"v":10,"ref":"2Cor 7:10","grc":"ἡ γὰρ κατὰ θεὸν λύπη μετάνοιαν εἰς σωτηρίαν ἀμεταμέλητον ⸀ἐργάζεται· ἡ δὲ τοῦ κόσμου λύπη θάνατον κατεργάζεται.","lemmas":["ὁ","γάρ","κατά","θεός","λύπη","μετάνοια","εἰς","σωτηρία","ἀμεταμέλητος","ἐργάζομαι","δέ","κόσμος","θάνατος","κατεργάζομαι"],"tr":"For the sorrow according to God works a change of mind into unregretful salvation, but the sorrow of the world produces death.","para":null,"para_continued":false,"words":[{"form":"ἡ","lemma":"ὁ"